<L>__{exterior train station later that morning}
<A>__{a whistle blows. their luggage already aboard, francis, nikki, shep and bill walk down the platform, parallel to the train. bill claps his hands exuberantly.}
<C>__{bill}
<D>__{there she is, boys! the sud express!}
<C>__{shep}
<D>__{can you imagine cary tryin' to run away and leave us behind?}
